title: Intermediate Twisted Treeline bots not working
body:
Hi I'm level 10 and intermediate bots in TT queue is not working, the timer keeps going and won't match me with anyone. Can Riot fix this? I paid for xp boost

Thanks

replies.body: At your current level, more players might be queuing up for beginner bots or a different mode so the queue might take a little bit longer.  You could have also lost sync with matchmaking as well, so I recommend restarting your client just in case to make sure your network is keeping comms with our services.  I hope that helps!

Nah the queue is actually broken (at least on eune). Estimated: 3:00 but u actually have to wait over 15minutes "LITTLE bit longer" to find teammates and the level doesnt matter since i tried on my main and a new account.
when i was level 5 or below 5, i was able to play intermediate but not anymore which is weird. i couldn't play beginner level, only intermediate pre-10
